item.description:
Join us for a fun night of karaoke at The Golden Leaf in Boston- conveniently located near Chinatown. We are renting our own private room for 2 hours and will be having a blast! Full cash bar available. Don't miss this great night- singing, drinking, hanging out and having fun!

More info on pre-karaoke dinner nearby will be posted shortly as a separate meet up.

Please note that there is a room rental charge which will be divided equally among everyone attending- approx. $10 per person (cash). Since there is a rental charge for our group, please only sign up if you are definitely able to attend. If you RSVP "yes" and do not attend, you will be removed from the group.

If you have trouble finding our group, please call Catherine at 774 232 0000.
Look forward to seeing you there!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) inside ent. If need to, please call 774 232 0000
item.name: Karaoke Night at The Golden Leaf, Boston. Private Room Just for Us!
